\dfrac{\sqrt{x+2}-3}{\sqrt{x-3}-2}=\dfrac{\sqrt{x+2}-3}{\sqrt{x-3}-2}\dfrac{\sqrt{x+2}+3}{\sqrt{x-3}+2}\dfrac{\sqrt{x-3}+2}{\sqrt{x+2}+3}=\dfrac{x-7}{x-7}\dfrac{\sqrt{x-3}+2}{\sqrt{x+2}+3}=\dfrac{\sqrt{x-3}+2}{\sqrt{x+2}+3}
 \lim_{x\to 7}\frac{\frac{1}{2\sqrt{x+2}}}{\frac{1}{2\sqrt{x-3}}}\\ =\lim_{x\to 7}\frac{\sqrt{x-3}}{\sqrt{x+2}}\\ =\frac{2}{3} 
